{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"dtd359ji62c9elhzgyf75nc","title":"Template Tag","desc":"","updated":1641272664803,"created":1641105063906,"stub":false,"isDir":false,"custom":{"stub":false,"isDir":false},"fname":"s.m.html.tags.body.template-tag","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"DevLog"},"contentHash":"21281782c7bfef95bac5728039e40166","links":[{"from":{"fname":"s.l.javascript.template-cloning","vaultName":"DevLog"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":23,"offset":90},"end":{"line":7,"column":58,"offset":125},"indent":[]},"value":"s.m.html.tags.body.template-tag","alias":"s.m.html.tags.body.template-tag"}],"anchors":{"what-is-it-and-what-is-it-good-for":{"type":"header","text":"What is it and what is it good for","value":"what-is-it-and-what-is-it-good-for","line":11,"column":0,"depth":2},"how-to-use-it":{"type":"header","text":"How to use it","value":"how-to-use-it","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ntmymmerh3n4b7n007lnkbh","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"template-tag\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#template-tag\"></a>Template Tag</h1>\n<h2 id=\"what-is-it-and-what-is-it-good-for\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#what-is-it-and-what-is-it-good-for\"></a>What is it and what is it good for</h2>\n<p>Adding lots of little tags can get very cumbersome and error prone in JavaScript, so the less HTML tags we need to write in JavaScript the better.</p>\n<p>One way to do this is with the Template tag. The content does not render by default but is accessible by JavaScript for modification, Duplication, and more.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item 1: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item 2: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Want to easily add another <code>&#x3C;li></code> element to the list? Instead of using JavaScript to write the HTML code we can just use the Template:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item 1: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item 2: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use-it\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#how-to-use-it\"></a>How to use it</h2>\n<p>Need be able to grab the elements so we assign some classes and id's</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>ul</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>list<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item 1: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item 2: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>add-item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Add Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>template</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>list-item-template<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>title<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Item: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Now to access it</p>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> template <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token dom variable\">document</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'list-item-template'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> list <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token dom variable\">document</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'list'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token dom variable\">document</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'add-item'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> itemCount <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> list<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">children</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">length</span>\n\nbutton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> item <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> template<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">cloneNode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  itemCount<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n  item<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">innerText</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Item </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>itemCount<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">: </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n  item<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.content'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">innerText</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Content </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>itemCount<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n  list<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token method function property-access\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>Reference:\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.webdevsimplified.com/2020-06/template-tag/\">https://blog.webdevsimplified.com/2020-06/template-tag/</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/DevLog/notes/q2ztzumj77mv802iur869do\">Template Cloning (DevLog)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"ro